
{center}
{subhead} Highlights of next issue{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

Yes, we will be back next year, bigger and brighter than ever, issue
20 will kick off the new year and be the first issue of AIO in the year 
1999, it will be available {bold}Saturday 23rd January 1999{nobold}.
{p} {p}
We will be bringing you all the latest news and reviews, obviously
we'll slip in a few interviews and other great things to make the new
year a truly special one.
{p} {p}
The winners of the Christmas competitions will be announced along side
a full review of Wasted Dreams from Vulcan if it gets released in time
and some other behind the scenes articles like the article on the Amiga
in 19 different countrys.
{p} {p}
If you have a moment please drop us an email at {bold}amiga@thefree.net{nobold} letting
us know what you think of this new GUI and we'll print it next issue for
the whole world to see, you can ofcourse write us letters on any other
topic and we'll include them also.
{p} {p}
Hope you have a great Christmas!{p}
Chris Seward